It's a design pattern where an object (aka "observable" or "publisher") maintain a list of dependents (called "observers")
and automatically notifies dependants / observers whenever there is a change in its state

2 models

Push: Observable pushes the data it want to the observer to receive
Pull: Observer holds observable object reference and when it got to know something updated, it pulls the data whatever it needs using observable object


